Build Status

   A curated collection of awesome web typography articles.

Articles

     * [https://calendar.perfplanet.com/2016/no-font-face-bulletproof-synt
       ax/]No @font-face Syntax will ever be Bulletproof, Nor Should It Be
     * [https://www.zachleat.com/web/rename-font/]Font Aliasing, or how to
       rename a font in CSS
     * [https://viljamis.com/2016/the-future-of-web-fonts/]The Future of
       Web Fonts
     * [https://medium.com/@xtianmiller/your-body-text-is-too-small-5e02d3
       6dc902#.w1wdaeqzo]Your Body Text Is Too Small
     * [https://css-tricks.com/methods-controlling-spacing-web-typography/
       ]Methods for Controlling Spacing in Web Typography
     * [http://practicaltypography.com/bold-or-italic.html]Bold or Italic
     * [https://alistapart.com/article/webfonts-on-the-prairie]Webfonts on
       the Prairie
     * [https://medium.engineering/typography-is-impossible-5872b0c7f891#.
       5tnat6wy5]Typography is impossible
     * [https://robinrendle.com/essays/new-web-typography/]The New Web
       Typography
     * [https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2016/03/meaningful-web-typography
       /]Tools And Resources For A More Meaningful Web Typography
     * [http://typecast.com/blog/a-more-modern-scale-for-web-typography]A
       more modern scale for Web Typography
     * [http://www.creativebloq.com/typography/better-web-typography-few-s
       imple-steps-5132803]Better web typography in 13 simple steps
     * [http://www.creativebloq.com/web-design/choose-web-fonts-1233034]Ch
       oosing web fonts: 15 expert tips
     * [https://www.smashingmagazine.com/2014/12/the-good-the-bad-and-the-
       great-examples-of-web-typography/]The Good, The Bad And The Great
       Examples Of Web Typography
     * [https://www.w3.org/wiki/Typography_on_the_Web]W3C Typography on
       the Web
     * [https://www.igvita.com/2012/09/12/web-fonts-performance-making-pre
       tty-fast/]Web Fonts Performance: Making Pretty, Fast
     * [https://davidwalsh.name/font-smoothing]Font Smoothing
     * [https://dev.opera.com/articles/state-of-web-type/]The State of Web
       Type
     * [https://viljamis.com/dashes/]Dashes in Web Typography
     * [http://lamb.cc/typograph/]Scale & Rhythm in Typography
     * [http://retinart.net/typography/typographicscale/]Typographic Scale
     * [https://pearsonified.com/2011/12/golden-ratio-typography.php]The
       Mathematical Symphony of Typography
     * [https://blog.spoongraphics.co.uk/articles/the-best-free-alternativ
       es-to-the-most-popular-fonts]The Best Free Alternatives to the Most
